      "text": "やあ、この間ぶりだね\n三枝さんとこの新米プロデューサーくん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ nice seeing you again.\nRookie producer from Saegusa-san’s agency.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "先日はありがとう\n新米なのは正しいけどマネージャーなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for the other day.\nI may be a rookie‚ but I’m a manager not a producer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 15.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "肩書きなんてどうでもいいよ\nレッスン場使わせてもらうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Never mind your title.\nI’m going to use the lesson studio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、まだウチの子達が使ってて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ my girls are still in there…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 21.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "隅っこで勝手にやってるから\n気にしないでいいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll just use the corner.\nDon’t mind me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirの井川葵が練習してるのに\n気にしない訳ないだろう？　もうちょっと待ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course they’ll mind if Aoi Igawa from LizNoir\nis practicing next to them. Please‚ they’ll be done in a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 30.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "大げさだなぁ\nじゃあ外でやってるから空いたら教えてくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Overreacting.\nFine‚ I’ll warm up outside. Let me know when the studio is free.",
        "id": ""
